TIPS

To deploy the site in shared host:

>zip all files in only one file.zip
>create an folder in root folder with name "laravel" or other name.
>unzip all files in folder laravel
>move the content of public folder to public_html folder
>edit the file index.php, change the:
		require __DIR__.'/../bootstrap/autoload.php';
		to
		require __DIR__.'/../laravel/bootstrap/autoload.php';
		and
		$app = require_once __DIR__.'/../bootstrap/app.php';
		to
		$app = require_once __DIR__.'/../laravel/bootstrap/app.php';
>change the permissions of the public_html folder to 750.
>change the permissions of the index.php file to 644.
>enjoy.

